@startuml
title UML State Machine Diagram - Website Development

state HomePage
HomePage : do / Display homepage
HomePage : exit / Navigation bar available

state ProjectSelection
ProjectSelection : entry / User selects project
ProjectSelection : do / Display project information
ProjectSelection : exit / Return to HomePage

state MediaChoice
MediaChoice : entry / User chooses media type
MediaChoice : do / Display photos or videos
MediaChoice : exit / Return to ProjectSelection

state CareerOpportunities
CareerOpportunities : entry / User selects career opportunities
CareerOpportunities : do / Display job updates and application forms
CareerOpportunities : exit / Return to HomePage

state JobApplicationChecking
JobApplicationChecking : entry / Submitted job applications
JobApplicationChecking : do / Check submitted applications
JobApplicationChecking : exit / Return to CareerOpportunities

HomePage --> ProjectSelection
ProjectSelection --> MediaChoice
MediaChoice --> CareerOpportunities
CareerOpportunities --> JobApplicationChecking
JobApplicationChecking --> HomePage
@enduml
